      "content": "i mean yeah... exactly. i feel like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. i spend all day staring at his empty chair and it feels like there's no reason to even keep doing this. like, what am i even waiting for? for the pain to just get better? it doesn't feel like it's ever going to get better.",
